Components
Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04)
Buzzer
LED
Connections
Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04)
VCC: Connect to 5V on the Arduino.
GND: Connect to GND on the Arduino.
Trig: Connect to digital pin 3 on the Arduino (trigPin).
Echo: Connect to digital pin 2 on the Arduino (echoPin).
Buzzer
Positive (longer leg): Connect to digital pin 10 on the Arduino (buzzer).
Negative (shorter leg): Connect to GND on the Arduino.
LED
Anode (longer leg): Connect to digital pin 13 on the Arduino (ledPin) through a resistor.
Cathode (shorter leg): Connect to GND on the Arduino.
